item.title: A Little About Me
item.author: cooper.wallace5@gmail.com (Cooper Wallace)
item.description: Hey There, I’m Cooper! I’m currently studying for a B.Sc in Computer Science at MacEwan University. I have a strong passion for many areas in Computer Science, and I’m always trying to learn something new. This is a blog where I plan to share my experiences about what I’ve been working on, and things that other people may find useful. I hope that you enjoy the blog.
